<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FoodShare - Share Food, Share Love</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com/" crossorigin="" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Epilogue:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo-container">
                <div class="logo-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path d="M6 6H42L36 24L42 42H6L12 24L6 6Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2>FoodShare</h2>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <div class="nav-links">
                    <a href="/">How it works</a>
                    <a href="#">Get food</a>
                    <a href="#">Give food</a>
                    <a href="/#volunteer">Volunteer</a>
                </div>
                <div class="auth-buttons">
                    <button class="btn-primary">
                        <a href="/login">Sign in</a>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn-secondary">
                        <a href="/register">Sign up</a>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main>
            <section class="hero">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <h1>Share more, waste less</h1>
                    <p>We make it easy to share your extra food with your community. Whether you're an individual, a business, or a nonprofit, we have a solution for you.</p>
                    <button class="btn-primary">
                        <a href="/register">Get started</a>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="features">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24px" height="24px" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
                            <path d="M72,104a8,8,0,0,1,8-8h96a8,8,0,0,1,0,16H80A8,8,0,0,1,72,104Zm8,40h96a8,8,0,0,0,0-16H80a8,8,0,0,0,0,16ZM232,56V208a8,8,0,0,1-11.58,7.15L192,200.94l-28.42,14.21a8,8,0,0,1-7.16,0L128,200.94,99.58,215.15a8,8,0,0,1-7.16,0L64,200.94,35.58,215.15A8,8,0,0,1,24,208V56A16,16,0,0,1,40,40H216A16,16,0,0,1,232,56Zm-16,0H40V195.06l20.42-10.22a8,8,0,0,1,7.16,0L96,199.06l28.42-14.22a8,8,0,0,1,7.16,0L160,199.06l28.42-14.22a8,8,0,0,1,7.16,0L216,195.06Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Post Food</h2>
                    <p>In just a few taps, let us know what you have to share. We'll help you find a local organization that can put it to good use.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24px" height="24px" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
                            <path d="M188,80a27.79,27.79,0,0,0-13.36,3.4,28,28,0,0,0-46.64-11A28,28,0,0,0,80,92v20H68a28,28,0,0,0-28,28v12a88,88,0,0,0,176,0V108A28,28,0,0,0,188,80Zm12,72a72,72,0,0,1-144,0V140a12,12,0,0,1,12-12H80v24a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V92a12,12,0,0,1,24,0v28a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V92a12,12,0,0,1,24,0v28a8,8,0,0,0,16,0V108a12,12,0,0,1,24,0Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Claim Food</h2>
                    <p>Find food near you that's available for pickup. You can claim as much or as little as you need.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24px" height="24px" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256">
                            <path d="M247.42,117l-14-35A15.93,15.93,0,0,0,218.58,72H184V64a8,8,0,0,0-8-8H24A16,16,0,0,0,8,72V184a16,16,0,0,0,16,16H41a32,32,0,0,0,62,0h50a32,32,0,0,0,62,0h17a16,16,0,0,0,16-16V120A7.94,7.94,0,0,0,247.42,117ZM184,88h34.58l9.6,24H184ZM24,72H168v64H24ZM72,208a16,16,0,1,1,16-16A16,16,0,0,1,72,208Zm81-24H103a32,32,0,0,0-62,0H24V152H168v12.31A32.11,32.11,0,0,0,153,184Zm31,24a16,16,0,1,1,16-16A16,16,0,0,1,184,208Zm48-24H215a32.06,32.06,0,0,0-31-24V128h48Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2>Deliver Food</h2>
                    <p>Help get food from donors to recipients. You can deliver whenever and wherever works for you.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="users">
                <h1>Who can use FoodShare?</h1>
                <p>Our platform is designed to help individuals, businesses, and nonprofits share food with their communities. Here's how it works for each group:</p>
                
                <div class="user-cards">
                    <div class="user-card">
                        <div class="user-image individual"></div>
                        <h3>For individuals</h3>
                        <p>Got extra food? Share it with neighbors in need.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="user-card">
                        <div class="user-image business"></div>
                        <h3>For businesses</h3>
                        <p>Restaurants, grocery stores, and other businesses can use FoodShare to donate surplus food to local organizations.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="user-card">
                        <div class="user-image nonprofit"></div>
                        <h3>For nonprofits</h3>
                        <p>Local organizations can use FoodShare to receive donations and connect with volunteers who can help distribute food.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="cta">
                <h1>Ready to start sharing?</h1>
                <button class="btn-primary">
                    <a href="/register">Get started</a>
                </button>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>